注意事项：
	修订集：bfb41cc64197（4830）

	env.sh 添加配置：
		export OWL_FEEDBACK_TO_EMAIL='connect@learnonenglish.com'
		export OWL_REGISTRATION_FROM_EMAIL='registration@learnonenglish.com'

	1、pip install -r requirements/prod.txt
	2、python manage.py migrate --list
		确定有如下修订集：
		card 0004, 0005,0006
	3、python manage.py migrate owl.card
	4、python manage.py syncdb
	5、python manage.py migrate 执行其他migrations
	6、django-modeltranslation相关:
		python manage.py sync_translation_fields
		python manage.py update_translation_fields

	7、翻译所有tag
		python -c 'from owl.utils.translator import translate_all_tags;translate_all_tags()'
	7、python manage.py compress
	8、python manage.py collectstatic --ignore=*.scss
